extends layout

block content
  .container.mt-4
    h1 Create New File
    form(action="/files/create-new" method="post")
      .form-group
        label(for="fileName") File Name (end in .docx for a Word, .xlsx for Excel, .pptx for PowerPoint.)
        input#fileName.form-control(type="text" name="fileName" required=true placeholder="Enter file name")

      button.btn.btn-primary(type="submit") Create and edit file

    p.h3 Notes 
    p If you don't include an office extension, the system generally won't know how to work with the file. This includes edit, preview, pdf, and more.
    
